### Doctor-Patient Management System API Tests
### REST Client Extension (VS Code)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

---
### 1. Register a new Patient
# @name registerPatient
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rahul Verma",
  "email": "rahul.verma01@testmail.com",
  "phone": "9123456780",
  "dob": "1998-08-21",
  "password": "rahulPass@123"
}

---
### 2. Login as Patient
# @name loginPatient
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rahul.verma01@testmail.com",
  "password": "rahulPass@123"
}

@patientToken = {{loginPatient.response.body.token}}

---
### 3. Get Patient Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 4. Login Admin (Seed User)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@system.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

---
### 5. Create a Doctor (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. Anjali Mehta",
  "email": "anjali.mehta@healthcare.com",
  "specialty": "Dermatology",
  "qualifications": "MBBS, MD Dermatology",
  "experience": 8,
  "fees": 700,
  "clinic": "SkinCare Clinic",
  "gender": "Female"
}

---
### 6. Search Doctors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/doctors?specialty=Dermatology
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 7. Get Specific Doctor Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/doctors/1
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 8. Admin Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---
### 9. Doctor Login (Use temp password returned in Step 5)
# @name loginDoctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "anjali.mehta@healthcare.com",
  "password": "TEMP_PASSWORD_FROM_STEP_5"
}

@doctorToken = {{loginDoctor.response.body.token}}

---
### 10. Doctor Changes Password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/password
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "TEMP_PASSWORD_FROM_STEP_5",
  "newPassword": "DoctorSecure@456"
}

---
### 11. Doctor Creates Slot
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-04-02T00:00:00.000Z",
  "startTime": "2026-04-02T11:00:00.000Z",
  "endTime": "2026-04-02T11:30:00.000Z"
}

---
### 12. Doctor Views Slots
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

---
### 13. Doctor Deletes Slot
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/slots/2
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

---
### 14. Admin Views Doctors
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---
### 15. Admin Views Patients
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---
### 16. Admin Views Appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---
### 17. Patient Books Appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotId": 2,
  "clientTime": "2026-04-02T11:00:00.000Z"
}

---
### 18. Patient Appointment History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 19. Patient Cancels Appointment
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/appointments/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 20. Doctor Views Appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

---
### 21. Doctor Updates Appointment Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/appointments/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}